oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry star Kitty Wells with Johnny Wright and Bill Phillips at the Northmor School
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Wells, Kitty
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Grand Ole Opry stars Kitty Wells, Johnny Wright, Bill Phillips, Ken Allen, Doug Jones, and the Tennessee Mountain Boys at the Northmor School on April 25. Poster features metal photoplates of Kitty Wells, Johnny Wright, Bill Phillips, Ken Allen, and Doug Jones.
